        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>lighting devices by function [300179871], lighting devices [300037581], lighting equipment [300428218], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
